2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-at-sea-cruises-canceled-no-ship-miray-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20New%20Jersey%20city%20hasn't%20had%20a%20single%20traffic%20death%20in%20almost%207%20years.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hoboken%20bike%20lane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656122414ca513d8242e5e8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENearly%20half%20of%20the%20streets%20in%20Hoboken%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20have%20bike%20lanes.%20The%20infrastructure%20is%20part%20of%20the%20city's%20effort%20to%20eliminate%20traffic%20deaths.%3Cp%3EEduardo%20Munoz%20Alvarez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20traffic%20deaths%20are%20way%20up%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Hoboken%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20go%20years%20without%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20mayor%20and%20head%20of%20transportation%20credit%20a%20slew%20of%20road%20improvements%20and%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20include%20lowering%20speed%20limits%20and%20installing%20new%20crosswalks%2C%20curb%20extensions%2C%20and%20bike%20lanes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvehicle-related-deaths-increase-car-safety-pedestrians-cyclists-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20roads%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20dangerous%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202019%20and%202022%2C%20traffic%20fatalities%20jumped%2018%25%2C%20with%20pedestrian%20deaths%20hitting%20a%2040-year%20high%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Governors%20Highway%20Safety%20Association.%20Authorities%20blame%20the%20increased%20fatalities%20on%20speeding%2C%20impaired%20driving%2C%20and%20people%20not%20wearing%20seatbelts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20New%20Jersey%20city%20is%20bucking%20the%20trend.%20In%20Hoboken%2C%20local%20leaders%20have%20invested%20in%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20cut%20road%20deaths%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it's%20working.%20The%20city%20hasn't%20had%20a%20single%20traffic%20death%20since%20January%202017%2C%20and%20traffic%20injuries%20have%20declined%20about%2040%25%20in%20that%20period%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-11-20%2Fthis-new-jersey-mayor-ended-traffic-deaths-with-a-vision-zero-plan%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dcitylab%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dsocialflow-organic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoboken%20Mayor%20Ravi%20Bhalla%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20in%202017%2C%20started%20the%20city's%20Vision%20Zero%20effort%20in%202019.%20The%20project%20has%20an%20ambitious%20goal%20of%20eliminating%20all%20traffic%20deaths%20and%20injuries%20n%20the%20city%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoboken%20has%20since%20pursued%20a%20slew%20of%20measures%20to%20calm%20traffic%2C%20and%20design%20roads%20and%20intersections%20to%20promote%20safety%2C%20while%20encouraging%20residents%20to%20bike%2C%20walk%2C%20or%20take%20public%20transit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoboken%20lowered%20its%20speed%20limit%20to%2020%20mph%20citywide%20in%202022.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Funsafe-at-many-speeds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20has%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20speed%20a%20vehicle%20is%20traveling%20at%20when%20it%20hits%20a%20pedestrian%20has%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20how%20deadly%20the%20accident%20is.%20While%20a%20pedestrian%20who's%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20traveling%20at%2020%20mph%20has%20a%2093%25%20rate%20of%20survival%2C%20the%20survival%20rate%20drops%20to%2080%25%20when%20the%20vehicle%20is%20going%2030%20mph.%20Both%20death%20and%20injury%20rates%20continue%20to%20rise%20as%20speeds%20climb%20above%2030%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20also%20installed%20new%20crosswalks%2C%20bike%20lanes%2C%20and%20curb%20extensions%2C%20which%20prevent%20cars%20from%20parking%20or%20turning%20right%20next%20to%20the%20corners%20of%20sidewalks%20at%20intersections.%20Known%20as%20%26quot%3Bdaylighting%2C%26quot%3B%20these%20curb%20extensions%20provide%20more%20visibility%20to%20pedestrians%20and%20drivers%20at%20crosswalks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhalla%20introduced%20Citi%20Bike%20%E2%80%94%20the%20popular%20bike-sharing%20program%20%E2%80%94%20in%202021%2C%20and%20Hoboken%20now%20has%20bike%20lanes%20on%20almost%20half%20of%20its%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20behind%20Hoboken's%20Vision%20Zero%20is%20to%20make%20its%20streets%20less%20car-focused%2C%20and%20more%20welcoming%20and%20accessible%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20transport%2C%20Bhalla%20told%20Bloomberg%20CityLab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20improvements%20start%20out%20simple%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0sometimes%20all%20that's%20required%20is%20a%20little%20sidewalk%20paint%2C%20he%20said.%20Sturdier%20and%20more%20expensive%20road%20alterations%20come%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20with%20a%20bucket%20of%20paint%2C%20you%20can%20actually%20create%20a%20curb%20extension%3B%20you%20can%20create%20high%20visibility%20crosswalks%2C%20which%20create%20a%20much%20safer%20environment%20at%20a%20very%20cheap%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhalla%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20when%20you%20do%20the%20next%20iteration%20of%20repaving%2C%20you%20can%20really%20amplify%20and%20increase%20on%20those%20improvements%20that%20you've%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoboken%20began%20by%20piloting%20these%20changes%20and%20then%20polled%20residents%2C%20who%20supported%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20was%20to%20make%20complete%20streets%20components%20as%20fundamental%20as%20a%20centerline%20or%20an%20ADA%20ramp%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoboken's%20director%20of%20transportation%20and%20parking%2C%20Ryan%20Sharp%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbikeportland.org%2F2023%2F04%2F26%2Fhoboken-leader-shares-secret-sauce-for-vision-zero-success-373939%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20transportation%20summit%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20additions%20like%20bike%20lanes%20have%20grown%20in%20popularity%2C%20city%20council%20members%20who%20initially%20opposed%20them%20have%20changed%20their%20tune%2C%20Sharp%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoboken-nj-eliminated-traffic-deaths-bikes-road-paint-speed-limit-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700864886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6561235c22cf74a5739c4b40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoboken-nj-eliminated-traffic-deaths-bikes-road-paint-speed-limit-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Traffic%20deaths%20have%20surged%20across%20the%20US%20in%20recent%20years.%20But%20Hoboken%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20has%20bucked%20the%20trend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoboken-nj-eliminated-traffic-deaths-bikes-road-paint-speed-limit-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jubilation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20in%20defiance%20of%20Israeli%20orders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700864640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-israel-west-bank-prisoners_6371311.jpg%3F20231124224017%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjubilation-in-the-west-bank-in-defiance-of-israeli-orders-as-palestinian-prisoners-freed-13015486%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20delivered%20its%20side%20of%20the%20bargain%20in%20scenes%20of%20chaos.