0exchange%2C%20150%20Palestinians%20prisoners%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2039%20released%20on%20Friday%2C%2028%20were%20freed%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20an%20AFP%20correspondent%20saw%2C%20while%20the%20other%2011%20were%20on%20their%20way%20to%20annexed%20east%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20broke%20through%20Gaza's%20militarised%20border%20with%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20to%20kill%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20about%201%2C200%20people%20and%20seize%20around%20240%20Israeli%20and%20foreign%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Going%20home'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pause%20in%20fighting%20triggered%20a%20mass%20movement%20of%20thousands%20of%20Gazans%20who%20had%20sought%20refuge%20in%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20from%20relentless%20Israeli%20bombardment%20begun%20after%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Omar%20Jibrin%2C%2016%2C%20told%20AFP%20after%20he%20emerged%20from%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20where%20he%20and%20eight%20family%20members%20had%20sought%20refuge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20in%20southern%20Gaza%20where%20many%20Palestinians%20fled%2C%20a%20cacophony%20of%20car%20horns%20and%20ambulance%20sirens%20has%20replaced%20the%20sound%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Khaled%20al-Halabi%2C%20the%20truce%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20chance%20to%20breathe%26quot%3B%20after%20nearly%20seven%20weeks%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalabi%20had%20taken%20refuge%20in%20Rafah%20but%20is%20from%20Gaza%20City%20in%20the%20north%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20retaliatory%20air%2C%20artillery%20and%20naval%20strikes%20alongside%20a%20ground%20offensive%20have%20killed%20about%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20the%20Hamas%20government%20in%20Gaza%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGazans%20have%20struggled%20to%20survive%20with%20shortages%20of%20water%20and%20other%20essentials.%20Trucks%20carrying%20aid%2C%20including%20fuel%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20food%2C%20began%20moving%20into%20Gaza%20through%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20from%20Egypt%20shortly%20after%20the%20truce%20began%20at%207%3A00%20am%20(0500%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJens%20Laerke%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20humanitarian%20agency%2C%20OCHA%2C%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20pause%20%26quot%3Bleads%20to%20a%20longer-term%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20repeated%20the%20need%20for%20access%20across%20Gaza%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20north%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20damage%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20needs%20are%20the%20greatest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%2C%201.7%20million%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20people%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20been%20displaced%20by%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20thousands%20of%20them%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20they%20loaded%20belongings%20onto%20carts%2C%20strapped%20them%20to%20car%20roofs%2C%20or%20slung%20bags%20over%20their%20shoulders%2C%20crowding%20streets%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20from%20temporary%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20warplanes%20dropped%20leaflets%20warning%20people%20that%20the%20war%20is%20not%20over%20and%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20dangerous%26quot%3B%20to%20return%20north%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20Israel's%20military%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce%20was%20also%20a%20chance%20for%20some%20Palestinians%20to%20return%20to%20Gaza%20through%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20a%20few%20apparent%20gunshots%20were%20heard%20and%20dark%20plumes%20of%20smoke%20rose%20periodically%20over%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20an%20AFPTV%20livecam%20showed%2C%20but%20the%20truce%20appeared%20to%20be%20holding%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarefully%20prepared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZiv%20Agmon%2C%20legal%20adviser%20to%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%2C%20told%20reporters%20before%20the%20hostages%20were%20freed%20that%20they%20would%20be%20received%20individually%20or%20in%20groups%20by%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20taken%20across%20the%20border%20and%20handed%20to%20the%20Israeli%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20El-Arish%2C%20in%20the%20Sinai%2C%20they%20would%20be%20flown%20to%20Israel%2C%20an%20Egyptian%20security%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgmon%20said%20soldiers%20had%20been%20carefully%20prepared%20to%20receive%20potentially%20deeply%20traumatised%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20medical%20examinations%2C%20the%20former%20captives%20will%20be%20able%20to%20telephone%20family%20members%20before%20reunions%20later%20at%20Israeli%20medical%20facilities%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20has%20confirmed%20the%20identities%20of%20210%20of%20the%20roughly%20240%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2035%20of%20those%20seized%20were%20children%2C%20with%2018%20of%20them%20aged%2010%20or%20under%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20abduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20earlier%20released%20four%20women%20and%20Israeli%20forces%20rescued%20another.%20Two%20other%20captives%2C%20including%20a%20woman%20soldier%2C%20were%20found%20dead%20by%20Israeli%20troops%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaayan%20Zin%2C%20whose%20eight-%20and%2015-year-old%20daughters%20Ela%20and%20Dafna%20are%20among%20the%20hostages%2C%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20that%20she%20had%20been%20informed%20their%20names%20were%20not%20on%20the%20list%20of%20those%20due%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20incredibly%20difficult%20for%20me%3B%20I%20long%20for%20their%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wr