0w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20versus%20RSS%20in%20Bhilwara%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMake%20your%20headline%20%E2%80%98BJP%20versus%20RSS%E2%80%99%20not%20%E2%80%98Congress%20versus%20BJP%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20advises%20Arun%20Vaishnav%2C%20an%20engineering%20student%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20heated%20political%20discussion%20with%20his%20friends%20outside%20Shagun%2C%20a%20sweet-shop%20in%20Bhilwara%20city%20which%20lies%20in%20the%20Mewar%20region%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20most%20residents%20of%20Bhilwara%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20electoral%20battle%20is%20down%20to%20in%20this%20%E2%80%98BJP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egarh%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20%E2%80%98fort%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20a%20Congress%20victory%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E1998%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20never%20lost%20this%20seat%20since%201980.%C2%A0%20It%20even%20extended%20this%20hold%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20Bhilwara%20district%20in%202018%2C%20winning%205%20of%20the%20seven%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20long%20while%2C%20the%20Congress%20feels%20it%20may%20have%20a%20chance%2C%20however%20slim%2C%20because%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20from%20an%20independent%20who%20is%20widely%20perceived%20to%20be%20backed%20by%20the%20RSS.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhilwara%20is%20one%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20most%20industrial%20towns%2C%20popularly%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CManchester%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%9D.%20Here%20the%20textile%20industry%2C%20known%20for%20both%20the%20manufacture%20of%20synthetic%20yarn%20and%20its%20processing%20units%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20employer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20brought%20a%20certain%20affluence%20and%20prominence%20to%20the%20merchant%20communities%20of%20the%20city%20like%20the%20Maheshwaris%2C%20who%20are%20numerically%20the%20second%20largest%20set%20of%20voters%20after%20the%20Brahmins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20Bhilwara%20MP%2C%20Subhash%20Baheria%2C%20is%20from%20the%20community%2C%20as%20have%20been%203%20MLAs%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20Other%20merchant%20community%20such%20as%20the%20Oswali%20Jains%20and%20Aggarwals%20are%20also%20largely%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20forming%20a%20committed%20urban%20Brahmin-Baniya%20base%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20base%20has%20been%20built%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20long%20history%20of%20work%20by%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99%20work%20in%20this%20region%2C%20one%20that%20long%20precedes%20Modi%2C%20and%20has%20earned%20Bhilwara%20the%20sobriquet%20%E2%80%9CSecond%20Nagpur%E2%80%9D.%20In%20this%20setting%20the%20challenge%20from%20Ashok%20Kothari%2C%20a%20Jain%2C%20is%20potent.%20Kothari%20is%20a%20businessman%20who%20runs%20a%20textile%20company%20and%20is%20known%20for%20setting%20up%20gaushalas%20to%20look%20after%20abandoned%20and%20ailing%20cows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20campaign%20pictures%2C%20Ashok%20Kothari%20is%20shown%20sporting%20a%20tilak%20with%20a%20cow%20in%20the%20background.%20His%20slogan%20and%20campaign%20songs%20reinforce%20his%20image%20as%20a%20gau-sewak%2C%20with%20the%20refrain%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAshok%20Kothari%20ko%20jeetao%2C%20Gau%20maata%20ko%20bachao%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Elect%20Ashok%20Kothari%2C%20Save%20the%20Cow)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepak%20Agarwal%2C%20a%20Kothari%20supporter%20who%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20earlier%2C%20explains%20his%20switch%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cselfless%20man%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20says%20it%20cares%20about%20cows%20but%20it%20is%20the%20RSS%20man%20who%20does%20real%20work%20with%20the%20gaushalas.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20how%20he%20knew%20Kothari%20was%20from%20the%20RSS%2C%20Deepak%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20the%20RSS%20will%20not%20openly%20say%20it%20is%20their%20candidate%2C%20its%20cadres%20do%20not%20even%20declare%20all%20the%20work%20it%20has%20done%20for%20the%20BJP%20candidates%20but%20ask%20anyone%20in%20Bhilwara%20and%20they%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%20who%20the%20RSS%20is%20working%20for%20this%20time%2C%20their%20own%20man%2C%20Ashok%20Kothari.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20little%20to%20distinguish%20between%20the%20campaigns%20of%20the%20two%20men%2C%20the%20saffron%20colours%20and%20flags%20have%20confused%20a%20few%20like%20Lalita%20Prajapat%2C%20who%20sells%20earthen-ware.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EShe%20says%20she%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20because%20of%20Modi%20and%20thought%C2%A0%20Ashok%20Kothari%20was%20the%20BJP%20candidate%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20done%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejan%20sabha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20he%20was%20wearing%20the%20BJP%20colours%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20saffron%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0everywhere%2C%20in%20his%20photos%2C%20stickers%20and%20he%20spoke%20of%20caring%20for%20gau-mata.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24143201%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.31.13.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24143201%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.31.13.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24143201%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.31.13-300x165.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24143201%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.31.13-1024x563.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686202%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22660%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalita%20Prajapat%20says%20she%E2%80%99s%20confused%20between%20both%20the%20saffron-wearing%20candidates%2C%20in%20a%20battle%20tag-lined%20%E2%80%98RSS%20vs%20BJP%E2%80%99%20in%20Bhilwara%20constituency.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20responses%20are%20why%20the%20BJP%20has%20spent%20the%20greater%20part%20of%20the%20campaign%20attacking%20Kothari%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20dividing%20Hindus%20to%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20Om%20Narayniwal.%20But%20few%20here%20believe%20the%20Congress%20will%20actually%20win%20the%20Bhilwara%20seat.%20The%20BJP%20candidate%20Vithal%20Shankar%20Awasthi%20is%20the%20sitting%20MLA%2C%20having%20won%20the%20past%20three%20assembly%20elections%20with%20a%20huge%20margin.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20got%2052%25%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20Brahmin%20organisations%20have%20already%20pledged%20their%20support%20to%20him%20while%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20been%20visiting%20Bhilwara%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20quell%20talk%20of%20a%20BJP-RSS%20rift.%20Speaking%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Bhilwara%20on%20November%2018%2C%20Arun%20Singh%2C%20the%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20denied%20any%20such%20rift.%20The%20BJP%20has%20also%20expelled%20some%20prominent%20workers%20for%20working%20with%20Ashok%20Kothari%20and%20threatened%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20others.%20Om%20Prakash%20Sharma%2C%20of%20the%20Sarv%20Brahmin%20Mahasabha%20feels%20Awasthi%20is%20in%20a%20comfortable%20position%2C%20hard%20to%20dislodge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20ultimate%20irony%2C%20residents%20of%20Bhilwara%20say%2C%20it%20is%20BJP%20workers%20who%20are%20sending%20Whatsapp%20forwards%20and%20Facebook%20posts%2C%20taking%20Kothari%20and%20his%20supporters%20to%20task%20for%20seeking%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20cow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Rana%20Pratap%E2%80%99s%20descendant%20now%20fights%20a%20different%20battle%20in%20Nathdwara%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRana%20Pratap%E2%80%99s%20descendant%20Vishwaraj%20Singhji%20Mewar%E2%80%99s%20battlefield%20is%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ones%20his%20ancestors%20fought%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pritam%2C%20pleased%20with%20his%20warrior%20metaphor.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPritam%2C%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20OBC%20caste%2C%20serves%20chai%20from%20his%20cart%20in%20Nathdwara%2C%20a%20temple%20town%20in%20Rajsamund%20district%20of%20the%20Mewar%20region%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20mistaken%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20simple%20battle%20between%20a%20raja%20and%20a%20rank.%20Both%20are%20rajas%2C%20one%20in%20the%20mahal%2C%20the%20other%20a%20raja%20of%20Mewar%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cpalace%20raja%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20Vishwaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20who%20comes%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Mewar%2C%20which%20ruled%20from%20Udaipur%2C%2045%20kms%20from%20Nathdwara.%20The%20title%20%E2%80%9CMaharana%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CRana%E2%80%9D%20has%20long%20been%20used%20by%20the%20Mewar%20royal%20family%20who%20see%20themselves%20as%20custodians%2C%20ruling%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Eklinji%2C%20a%20manifestation%20of%20Siva.%20This%20history%2C%20and%20their%20descent%20from%20the%20legendary%20warrior%20Rana%20Pratap%2C%20confers%20immense%20prestige%20and%20status%20on%20the%20Mewar%20royal%20household.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144302%2Fcp-joshi-campaigns-nathdwara.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144302%2Fcp-joshi-campaigns-nathdwara.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144302%2Fcp-joshi-campaigns-nathdwara-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144302%2Fcp-joshi-campaigns-nathdwara-1024x681.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686204%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFive-time%20MLA%2C%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20campaigns%20in%20Nathdwara.%20Photo%3A%20Paresh%20Pandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20title%20is%20held%20by%20Vishwaraj%E2%80%99s%20uncle%2C%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20but%20his%20father%2C%20Mahendra%20Singh%2C%20sees%20himself%20as%20the%20rightful%20heir.%20Mahendra%20Singh%20won%20the%201989%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20from%20Chittorgarh%20but%20two%20years%20later%20lost%20on%20Congress%20tickets%20from%20both%20Chittor%20and%20Bhilwara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20son%20now%20hopes%20to%20carry%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20mantle.%20His%20campaign%20chooses%20to%20invoke%20his%20royal%20heritage%20in%20every%20possible%20way.%20Chants%20of%20%E2%80%9CRana%20Pratap%20ki%20Jai%E2%80%9D%20serve%20as%20a%20constant%20reminder%20of%20the%20much-mythicised%20traditions%20of%20Rajput%20valour%20and%20glory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20state%20where%20feudalism%20has%20deep%20roots%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20BJP%20hopes%20the%20royal%20influence%2C%20and%20the%20caste%20equation%2C%20will%20work%20in%20Vishwaraj%E2%80%99s%20favour.%20Rajputs%20make%20up%20about%2070%2C000%20of%20the%20238%2C000%20voters%20in%20this%20constituency%2C%20and%20their%20vote%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20consolidating%20behind%20the%20BJP%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20no%20guarantee%20of%20victory.%20Vishwaraj%20is%20pitted%20against%20someone%20who%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CRaja%20of%20Mewar%20politics%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20stalwart%20C.P.%20Joshi%2C%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20Nathdwara%2C%20and%20a%20one-time%20MP%20from%20Bhilwara.%C2%A0%20People%20still%20recount%20how%20he%20lost%20the%202008%20Assembly%20election%2C%20painfully%2C%20by%20one%20vote%2C%20but%20admire%20his%20resilience%20in%20returning%20to%20contest%20and%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoshi%20is%20going%20into%20these%20elections%2C%20much%20like%20his%20party%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20work%20he%20says%20he%20have%20done.%20Even%20those%20supporting%20the%20BJP%20admit%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Joshi%20has%20created%20infrastructure%20in%20Nathdwara%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20roads%2C%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20chaat%20stall%2C%20near%20Lalbagh%20Gardens%2C%20the%20customers%20said%20they%20knew%20who%20Vishwaraj%20was%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20he%20would%20get%20much%20electoral%20traction%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%E2%80%99s%20from%20a%20Raj%20gharana%20so%20there%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20a%20buzz%20and%20some%20curiosity%20but%20he%20comes%20from%20Udaipur%2C%20most%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20him%20while%20C.P.%20Joshi%20is%20a%20local%20and%20has%20done%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%20Gayri%2C%20a%20Gujjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144437%2FVishwaraj-and-wife-Nathdwara.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144437%2FVishwaraj-and-wife-Nathdwara.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144437%2FVishwaraj-and-wife-Nathdwara-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24144437%2FVishwaraj-and-wife-Nathdwara-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686205%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVishwaraj%20and%20wife%20Nathdwara.%20Photo%3A%20Paresh%20Pandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJitender%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kotharia%20village%2C%20pulls%20up%20on%20his%20motorbike%20to%20speak%20to%20us.%C2%A0%20Pointing%20to%20a%20political%20hoarding%20with%20the%20picture%20of%20Vishwaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20prince%20of%20Mewar%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20great%20Rana%20Pratap%20but%20he%E2%80%99ll%20lose%20these%20elections%20as%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20him%20here.%E2%80%9D%20He%20quickly%20clarifies%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20vote%20for%20him%2C%20of%20course%20as%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20he%20pauses%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20from%20the%20Rajput%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Joshi%20seemed%20unfazed%20by%20the%20competition%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20legacy%20to%20his%20%5BVishwaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%5D%20family%2C%20there%20is%20no%20competition%20between%20my%20family%20and%20his%20family.%20He%20is%20from%20family%20of%20Maharana%20Pratap%2C%20we%20are%20all%20proud%20that%20he%20is%20from%20that%20legacy.%20But%20this%20election%20requires%20a%20person%20who%20is%20well%20exposed%20to%20electoral%20politics%2C%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20party%20and%20of%20this%20region%20so%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20why%20he%20opted%20for%20this.%20To%20me%20he%20seems%20like%20a%20gentleman.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENear%20the%20Purohit%20Dairy%2C%20a%20Brahmin%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Evoter%20pitches%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20from%20a%20great%20lineage%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Maharana%20Rana%20Pratap.%20All%20of%20Mewar%2C%20the%20country%20bows%20our%20head%20to%20this%20great%20warrior%20and%20we%20respect%20every%20one%20of%20his%20descendants.%20But%20as%20a%20descendant%20of%20Rana%20Pratap%2C%20perhaps%20Kunwar%20Vishvaraj%20should%20have%20contested%20from%20Udaipur%20city%2C%20or%20from%20Chittor%2C%20or%20from%20Haldi%20Ghati%20or%20from%20Kumbalgarh%2C%20why%20has%20he%20come%20to%20the%20Brahmins%20for%20votes%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20section%20of%20the%20Brahmins%20voters%20who%20number%2035-40%2C000%20could%20consolidate%20behind%20Joshi%2C%20leaving%20the%20result%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20non-%20upper-caste%20voters.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20the%20work%20Joshi%20has%20done%20that%20stand%20him%20in%20good%20stead.%C2%A0%20In%20some%20of%20the%20smaller%20villages%20adjacent%20to%20the%20town%2C%20among%20voters%20from%20Dalits%20and%20more%20marginalised%20OBC%20groups%20there%20are%20is%20clear%20evidence%20of%20support%20for%20Joshi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPramit%20from%20the%20Kumhar%20community%20sums%20up%20this%20battle%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20excited%20to%20see%20Mahrana%20of%20Mewar%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20who%20will%20win%2C%20but%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20no%20one%20has%20done%20as%20much%20work%20for%20Nathdwara%20as%20CP%20Joshi.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIAS%20vs%20IPS%20in%20Bassi%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20may%20not%20be%20a%20big%20city%20like%20Jaipur%20but%20in%20Bassi%20we%20are%20very%20intelligent%20voters%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eboth%20parties%20have%20given%20tickets%20to%20big%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramesh%20Meena%2C%20whose%20brother%20Dinesh%20was%20a%20sarpanch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20IAS%20vs%20IPS%20here%E2%80%9D%2C%20adds%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBassi%2C%20an%20assembly%20segment%20in%20Jaipur%20district%2C%20within%20the%20Dausa%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereserved%20tribal%20seat%2C%20just%2030%20kilometres%20from%20Jaipur%20city.%20Politics%20here%20revolve%20mainly%20around%20Meena%20candidates.%C2%A0%20The%20candidature%20of%20two%20bureaucrats%20points%20to%20the%20clout%20that%20the%20community%20enjoys%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20machinery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202008%2C%20the%20constituency%20has%20only%20elected%20independents.%20In%202018%2C%20a%20retired%20IPS%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eofficer%2C%20Laxman%20Meena%2C%20who%20took%20VRS%20in%202008%2C%20won%20as%20an%20independent%20with%20more%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethan%2048%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20after%20having%20finished%20third%20when%20he%20contested%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20in%202013.%20This%20time%20he%E2%80%99s%20fighting%20again%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20against%20a%20retired%20IAS%20officer%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandramohan%20Meena%2C%20who%20was%20State%20Information%20Commissioner%20from%202015%20to%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20of%20Bassi%20speak%20of%20the%20many%20things%20the%20two%20have%20in%20common.%C2%A0%2075-year-old%2C%20Kalyan%20Meena%2C%20says%20both%20the%20men%20have%20done%20Bassi%20proud%20before%20listing%20the%20similarities%2C%20of%20how%20both%20studied%20in%20the%20same%20school%20and%20college%2C%20were%20posted%20in%20various%20places%20in%20Rajasthan%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20know%20each%20other%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20thing%20going%20against%20the%20incumbent%20ex-IPS%20is%20his%20reputation%20for%20abrasiveness.%20A%20supporter%20offers%20an%20explanation%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20think%20Laxmanji%20can%20be%20rude%20but%20that%20only%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20some%20of%20his%20mannerisms%20get%20mistaken%20for%20rudeness.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20battle%20is%20further%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20bureaucrats%20are%20not%20the%20only%20Meenas%20in%20the%20fray.%20Jeetendra%20Meena%2C%20the%20former%20state%20president%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99%20ST%20Morcha%2C%20is%20contesting%20as%20an%20independent.%20He%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20on%2014%20November%20for%20filing%20his%20nomination%20against%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20official%20candidate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20people%20here%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20likely%20to%20get%20more%20than%208-10%2C%20000%20votes%20but%20if%20the%20contest%20is%20close%2C%20every%20vote%20may%20matter.%C2%A0%20In%20a%20constituency%20with%20an%20estimated%202%20lakh%20voters%2C%20the%20Meenas%20constitute%20about%2072%2C000.%20With%20these%20votes%20likely%20to%20be%20divided%20once%20again%20the%20outcome%20will%20hinge%20on%20how%20the%20other%20communities%20stack%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Arora%20Factor%20in%20Sri%20Ganganagar%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20you%20usually%20speak%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Jat%20factor%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Gujjar%20factor%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98or%20Rajput%20vote%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Dalit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Evote%E2%80%99%20here%20we%20speak%20of%20the%20Arora%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kuldeep%20Goyal%2C%20a%20journalist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebased%20in%20Sri%20Ganganagar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20northern%20most%20regions%2C%20Sri%20Ganganagar%2C%20like%20other%20neighbouring%20segments%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGanganagar%20and%20Hanumangarh%2C%20borders%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20Punjab.%20Here%20poll%20issues%20and%20caste%20equations%20overlap%20with%20those%20in%20Punjab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitics%20in%20this%20urban%20constituency%20here%20centres%20around%20the%20Aroras%20who%20are%20closely%20linked%20to%20the%20khatri%20castes%20of%20Punjab%2C%20the%20merchant%20baniya%20communities%20like%20the%20Agarwals%2C%20and%20the%20Brahmins.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20Ankur%20Manglani%20from%20the%20Arora%20community%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20Jaideep%20Bihani%20is%20from%20the%20merchant%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20other%20candidates%2C%20both%20Aroras%2C%20who%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20challenge%20the%20main%20party%20candidates%20%E2%80%93%20Dr%20Harish%20Raheja%2C%20a%20surgeon%20who%20runs%20a%20private%20hospital%20and%2055-year-old%20Karuna%20Ashok%20Chandak%2C%20the%20Nagar%20Parishad%20Sabhapati%20and%20wife%20of%20Ashok%20Chandak%20who%20contested%20and%20lost%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20in%202018.%20Karuna%20Chandak%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20rebel%20candidate%2C%20likely%20to%20undermine%20the%20Congress%20base.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Arora%20vote%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20about%2070-85%2C000%20of%20the%202%20lakh%20voters%2C%20is%20not%20consolidated%20behind%20one%20candidate.%20While%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20Ankur%20Maglani%20is%20also%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Arora%20Samaj%2C%20conflict%20within%20the%20Samaj%20has%20led%20to%20two%20Arora%20groups%2C%20with%20one%20going%20against%20Maglani%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20This%2C%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20local%20observers%2C%20has%20meant%20that%20the%20real%20fight%20here%20may%20well%20be%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Karuna%20Ashok%20Chandak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20in%20the%20fight%20over%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20community%2C%20governance%20itself%20take%20a%20backseat%20even%20when%20there%20is%20no%20shortage%20of%20fundamental%20issues.%C2%A0%20People%20here%20talk%20of%20water%20for%20both%20drinking%20and%20irrigation%20and%20complain%20that%20Punjab%20does%20not%20give%20Rajasthan%20its%20full%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eshare%20of%20water%2C%20%E2%80%9CPunjab%20has%20deliberately%20kept%20its%20irrigation%20channels%20kaccha%20so%20they%20say%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20release%20water%20in%20its%20full%20force%20but%20if%20Rajasthan%20can%20make%20its%20channels%20pucca%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPunjab%2C%20it%20is%20a%20ruse.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPunjab%20may%20not%20easily%20part%20with%20its%20water%20but%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20drug%20problem%20has%20filtered%20over.%20Drones%20are%20now%20thought%20to%20be%20dropping%20drugs%20from%20across%20the%20border%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20heroin%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20addicts%20have%20moved%20from%20using%20opium%20to%20heroin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20these%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20the%20one%20constant%2C%20praise%20for%20Gehlot%20and%20the%20work%20he%20has%20done.%20%E2%80%9CGovernment%20karamcharis%20are%20with%20Gehlot%20because%20of%20his%20pension%20scheme%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20advantage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20government%20employee%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20here%20remains%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20much%20of%20the%20state%2C%20is%20whether%20such%20work%20will%20be%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20Congress%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Rani%20versus%20rank%E2%80%99%20in%20Rajsamand%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2023%2C%20centennial%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20three-time%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20massive%20media%20gathered%20had%20their%20eyes%20and%20cameras%20trained%20on%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Jaipur%20royal%20family%20and%20an%20MP%20from%20Rajsamand%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20The%20function%20was%20held%20at%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%E2%80%99s%20memorial%20in%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20an%20assembly%20segment%20in%20Jaipur%20district%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20field%2052-year-old%20Diya%20Kumari%20had%20created%20much%20consternation%20within%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incumbent%20MLA%20from%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%2C%20Narpat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20Rajvi%2C%20now%20in%20his%20early%2070s%2C%20has%20held%20the%20seat%20for%20the%20BJP%20for%203%20terms%2C%20winning%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emassive%20margins%20and%20was%20expecting%20to%20be%20fielded%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDiya%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20at%20the%20memorial%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20bid%20to%20ensure%20all%20talk%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20Shekhawat%20family%20is%20buried.%20Narpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%20now%20faces%20an%20immensely%20tough%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eelectoral%20battle%20in%20Chittorgarh%20against%20a%20very%20popular%20BJP%20rebel%20candidate%20and%20sitting%20MLA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EChandrabhan%20Singh%20Akya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24145744%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.56.53.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24145744%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.56.53.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24145744%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.56.53-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24145744%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-2.56.53-1024x561.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22657%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDiya%20Kumari%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Jaipur%20campaigns%20in%20her%20constituency%2C%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20Jaipur.%20Photo%20%3A%20Niharika%20Popli%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20give%20Diya%20Kumari%20the%20ticket%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Rajsamand%2C%20when%20many%20felt%20it%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20Kiran%20Maheshwari%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20signalled%20her%20importance.%20Once%20seen%20as%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%20joined%20the%20party%20in%202013%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Scindia%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20then%20CM%20and%20then%20the%20prime-ministerial%20candidate%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20contested%20her%20first%20elections%20from%20Sawai%20Madhopur%20that%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETen%20years%20later%20she%E2%80%99s%20seen%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20choice%20to%20off-set%20the%20popularity%20of%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%2C%20who%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20Royal%E2%80%9D%20a%20common%20tagline%20for%20stories%20done%20on%20royal%20candidates%20each%20election.%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20comes%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20ruling%20family%20of%20Gwalior%2C%20is%20married%20into%20the%20Dholpur%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rift%20in%20the%20mentor-prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20relationship%2C%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%20has%20been%20a%20topic%20of%20much%20gossip%20and%20discussion%20in%20Jaipur.%20It%20became%20public%20in%202016%20when%20Diya%20Kumari%20and%20her%20mother%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Raje%20government%2C%20after%20the%20Jaipur%20Development%20Authority%20sealed%20off%20parts%20of%20their%20property%20during%20a%20demolition%20drive.%20Padmini%20Devi%2C%20Diya%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20even%20led%20a%20rally%20in%20protest%2C%20which%20was%20supported%20by%20other%20Rajput%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20interviews%20Diya%20Kumari%20assiduously%20avoids%20commenting%20on%20Raje%2C%20responding%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efamiliar%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20conflict%2C%20she%20is%20my%20senior%2C%E2%80%9D%20when%20we%20spoke%20to%20her%20during%20her%20early%20days%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20campaigning%20in%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CShe%E2%80%99s%20a%20beautiful%2C%20royal%20woman%20and%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20Chief%20Minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Geetanjal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECharan%2C%20who%20came%20to%20attend%20one%20of%20Diya%20Kumari%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20sabhas.%2