avardhan%20Rathore.%20The%20double%20trap%20shooter%20is%2C%20however%2C%20having%20to%20adjust%20his%20sights%20and%20take%20aim%20at%20a%20new%20target%20as%20he%20campaigns%20as%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20for%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20elections%20from%20the%20Jhotwara%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Jaisalmer%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20in%20January%201970%20to%20an%20Army%20Colonel%20and%20a%20teacher%2C%20Mr%20Rathore%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20National%20Defence%20Academy%20and%20then%20attended%20the%20Indian%20Military%20Academy.%20Commissioned%20in%20the%209th%20Grenadiers%20Regiment%20in%201990%2C%20he%20was%20stationed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20part%20of%20his%20career%20and%20was%20promoted%20to%20his%20final%20rank%20of%20Colonel%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rathore%20took%20up%20shooting%20as%20a%20sport%20in%201998%20and%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%202002%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20Manchester%2C%20setting%20a%20record%20of%20192%20for%20the%20event%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20broken.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first%20individual%20silver%20Olympic%20medallist%20in%20independent%20India%20by%20winning%20the%20medal%20in%20the%20double%20trap%20shooting%20event%20in%20the%202004%20Athens%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Entry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20the%20Army%2C%20Mr%20Rathore%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202013%20and%20described%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%26quot%3B%20leader%20who%20should%20be%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20lead%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20politics%20and%20politicians%20are%20hated%20but%20I%20still%20believe%20in%20goodness%20of%20a%20heart%20that%20has%20selfless%20intentions.%20With%20the%20grace%20of%20god%2C%20I%20will%20make%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathore%20had%20been%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A