%20were%20likely%20to%20be%20no%20major%20metal%20obstacles%20for%20the%20next%20five%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(a%20team%20of%20ground%20penetrating%20experts)%20could%20not%20say%20this%20with%20100%25%20accuracy%20but%20what%20they%20are%20expecting%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20continuous%20metal%20object%2C%20like%20girders%2C%20pipes%20and%20metal%20plates%2C%20in%20the%20next%205.4%20metres.%20They%20have%20pointed%20out%20some%20other%20hurdles%2C%20but%20this%20is%20good%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Uttarakhand%20Secretary%20Neeraj%20Khairwal%2C%20who%20is%20the%20nodal%20officer%20for%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%2C%20with%20the%20drill%20stopped%2C%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20manually%20inch%20closer%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20but%20the%20rescue%20is%20unlikely%20on%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20auger%20machine%20has%20encountered%20some%20difficulty%20again%20and%20that's%20why%20it's%20being%20dismantled.%20Simultaneously%2C%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20get%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20manually.%20We%20are%20analysing%20the%20debris%20and%20trying%20to%20figure%20this%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Workers%20Okay'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20workers%20are%20mentally%20stable%20and%20physically%20fit%20despite%20being%20trapped%20for%2013%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20adequately%20clothed%20and%20when%20we%20speak%20to%20them%2C%20they%20say%20they%20will%20walk%20out%20on%20their%20own.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20mental%20strength%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20labourers%20are%20also%20speaking%20to%20their%20families%20and%20one%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20before%2C%20has%20been%20helping%20his%20colleagues%20keep%20their%20morale%20high.%3C%2F