0day%2C%20she%20returned%20home%20running%20a%20high%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20it%20was%20regular%20flu.%20But%20when%20my%20parents%20took%20me%20to%20the%20doctor%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20I%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20ever%20again%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadaf%20was%20just%2010%20years%20old%20then.%20Instead%20of%20going%20to%20school%2C%20she%20started%20visiting%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20family%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20doctors%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20they%20went%20to%20Mumbai%20where%20surgery%20was%20performed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319444%2Fentrepreneur-with-rare-bone-disease-upcycles-newspaper-into-eco-friendly-dolls-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etreat%20her%20legs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20surgery%2C%20the%20doctor%20offered%20me%20%5Bspecially%20designed%5D%20shoes.%20With%20its%20help%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20take%20small%20steps.%20But%20those%20shoes%20were%20very%20heavy%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20discard%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsadaf-spices-2-1700831372.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Safat%20says%20her%20father%20was%20her%20only%20pillar%20of%20support.%20Except%20for%20him%2C%20everyone%20else%20doubted%20her%20capabilities.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsadaf-spices-2-1700831372.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsadaf-spices-2-1700831372-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsa