lakh%20and%20will%20be%20available%20in%20two%20colours%20-%20Slate%20Himalayan%20Salt%20and%20Slate%20Himalayan%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20variant%2C%20called%20Peak%2C%20has%20been%20priced%20at%202.79%20lakh%20for%20the%20Kamet%20White%20and%202.84%20lakh%20for%20Hanle%20Black.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20difference%20between%20all%20the%20variants%20is%20the%20colour.%20There%20are%20no%20mechanical%20or%20electronic%20differences%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-new%20Himalayan%2C%20also%20unofficially%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Himalayan%20450%2C%20is%20the%20successor%20to%20the%20first%20generation%20Royal%20Enfield%20Himalayan%20411%2C%20that%20came%20out%20in%202016.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20older%20motorcycle%20will%20be%20discontinued%20sometime%20after%20the%20new%20one%20rolls%20into%20showrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Himalayan%2C%20work%20on%20which%20started%20in%202017%2C%20is%20a%20grounds%20up%20model%20that%20Royal%20Enfield%20says%20shares%20not%20even%20a%20single%20bolt%20with%20its%20predecessor%2C%20and%20brings%20with%20it%20many%20firsts%20for%20the%20manufacturer.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20motorcycle%20is%20a%20new%20single-cylinder%20engine%20called%20the%20Sherpa%20450%20with%20a%20displacement%20of%20452%20cubic%20centimetres%2C%20is%20liquid%20cooled%2C%20has%20Dual%20Overhead%20Cams%20(DOHC)%2C%20an%20aluminium%20bore%2C%20a%20slightly%20short-stroke%20-%20all%20firsts%20for%20Royal%20Enfield.%20The%20new%20motor%20is%20also%2010%20kilos%20lighter%20than%20the%20previous%20model.%20This%20engine%20makes%2040%20PS%20of%20peak%20power%20and%2040%20Nm%20of%20peak%20torque%20-%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20a%20flat%20torque%20curve%20that%20makes%20the%20motorcycle%20extremely%20useable%20at%20both%20low%20and%20high%20revs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20list%20of%20firsts%20doesn't%20end%20there%20for%20Royal%20Enfield.%20The%20throttle%20has%20been%20changed%20from%20a%20cable-actuated%20one%20to%20a%20more%20sophisticated%20Ride-by%20Wire%20system%20that%20enables%20the%20motorcycle%20to%20have%20multiple%20riding%20modes%20(it%20has%20two%20-%20Performance%20and%20Economy%20-%20with%20the%20option%20to%20turn%20off%20ABS%20on%20the%20rear%20wheel%20in%20both%20the%20modes).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20has%20been%20paired%20with%20a%20six-speed%20gearbox%20and%20a%20slipper%20clutch.%20The%20motorcycle%20is%20capable%20of%20reaching%20speeds%20of%20about%20150%20kmph%20and%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20return%20a%20fuel%20economy%20figure%20of%20around%2028%20kmpl.%20It%20gets%20a%2017-litre%20fuel%20tank%20that%20should%20theoretically%20give%20it%20a%20travel%20range%20of%20about%20450%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20top%20model%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Kamet%20White%20and%20Hanle%20Black%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20top%20model%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Kamet%20White%20and%20Hanle%20Black%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F5mmt6vh8_himalayan-450-stock_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20model%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Kamet%20White%20and%20Hanle%20Black%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20previous%20Himalayan%20411%2C%20the%20wheel%20sizes%20have%20been%20retained%20as%2021%20inches%20front%20and%2017%20inches%20rear%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20wheels%20are%20aluminium%20(an%20option%20to%20switch%20to%20tubeless%20spoked%20rims%20will%20come%20later)%20and%20the%20rear%20tyre%20has%20been%20bumped%20up%20in%20width%20to%20140%20mm%20from%20120%20mm.%20The%20bike%20sports%20CEAT%20dual%20sport%20tyres%20that%20have%20been%20specially%20developed%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20has%20seen%20a%20massive%20bump-up%20too%20-%20while%20it%20retains%20the%20same%20travel%20at%20the%20front%2C%20200%20mm%2C%20the%20bike%20now%20sports%20Showa%20upside%20down%20front%20forks%2C%20which%20are%20a%20lot%20stiffer%20than%20the%20previous%20bike.%20At%20the%20rear%2C%20the%20suspension%20travel%20has%20increased%20from%20180%20to%20200%20mm%20in%20the%20new%20bike.%20The%20ground%20clearance%20too%20has%20seen%20a%20marginal%20increase%2C%20from%20220%20mm%20to%20230%20mm%20in%20the%20new%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20extensive%20changes%2C%20Royal%20Enfield%20has%20managed%20to%20shave%203%20kg%20from%20the%20previous%20bike%2C%20with%20the%20kerb%20weight%20of%20the%20new%20Himalayan%20now%20at%20196%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20motorcycle%20is%20clearly%20miles%20ahead%20of%20its%20predecessor%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seem%20how%20the%20market%20will%20react%20to%20the%20Himalayan%20450's%20pricing%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20motorcycles%20in%20the%20same%20price%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700836860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkrcee13g_royal-enfield-himalayan-450-650_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Froyal-enfield-himalayan-450-price-revealed-royal-enfield-all-new-himalayan-launched-priced-from-rs-2-69-lakh-4602233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weeks%20after%20officially%20unveiling%20the%20'all-new%20Himalayan'%2C%20Royal%20Enfield%20has%20now%20revealed%20the%20Indian%20pricing%20of%20their%20latest%20adventure%20motorcycle%20at%20their%20flagship%20event%20-%20Motoverse%20-%20in%20Goa%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Froyal-enfield-himalayan-450-price-revealed-royal-enfield-all-new-himalayan-launched-priced-from-rs-2-69-lakh-4602233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Froyal-enfield-himalayan-450-price-revealed-royal-enfield-all-new-himalayan-launch