alm%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20last%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20BCCI%20video%20after%20Thursday's%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Dhoni)%20told%20me%20to%20try%20to%20remain%20as%20calm%20as%20possible%20and%20try%20looking%20straight%20(at%20the%20bowler).%20That's%20how%20I%20tried%20to%20stay%20calm%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20did%20not%20mention%20when%20the%20discussions%20with%20Dhoni%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20a%20stiff%20target%20of%20209%2C%20India%20were%20reeling%20at%20154%20for%204%20in%20the%2015th%20over%20when%20Rinku%20walked%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20at%20the%20other%20end%20to%20support%20him%2C%20Rinku%20stayed%20calm%20and%20played%20smart%20cricket%20by%20rotating%20the%20strike%20and%20attacking%20the%20loose%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20batter%20remained%20not%20out%20on%2022%20off%2014%20balls%2C%20hitting%20four%20fours%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20157.14.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFeeling%20good%20that%20we%20won.%20My%20only%20aim%20was%20to%20be%20perfect%20when%20I%20walked%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20good%20out%20there%20to%20be%20playing%20alongside%20Surya.%20I%20was%20thinking%20of%20doing%20what%20I%20generally%20do%20in%20crunch%20situations%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20stay%20as%20calm%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20single%20needed%20off%20the%20final%20delivery%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sean%20Abbott%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106719-sean-abbott-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESean%20Abbott%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20deposited%20into%20the%20stands%20for%20a%20six%20by%20Rinku%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20big%20no-ball.%20Hence%2C%20the%20six%20was%20not%20counted%20but%20only%20the%20run%20off%20the%20no-ball%20was%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20realise%20it%20was%20a%20no-ball%20until%20I%20heard%20it%20from%20Axar%20bhai%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%20Although%20the%20winning%20six%20won't%20be%20considered%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%3B%20we%20won%20the%20match%2C%20that's%20what%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20Initially%20roped%20in%20by%20Kings%20XI%20Punjab%20(now%20Punjab%20Kings)%20for%20IPL%202017%2C%20he%20has%20been%20playing%20for%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20well%20in%20the%20IPL%202022%20and%20drew%20eyeballs%20in%20the%202023%20season%20for%20hammering%20five%20sixes%20in%20an%20over%20versus%20Gujarat%20Titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20IPL%20numbers%20read%20725%20runs%20in%2031%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2036.25%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20142.16%2C%20with%20four%20half-centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20he%20earned%20his%20Indian%20team%20call-up%20in%20August%20during%20the%20Ireland%20T20I%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20batted%20in%20just%20three%20T20I%20matches%2C%20amassing%2097%20at%20an%20average%20of%2097.0%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20194.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700835960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fnj974o7_ms-dhoni-rinku-singh-twitter_625x300_15_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flook-straight-at-ms-dhonis-career-changing-advice-to-rinku-singh-4603455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rinku%20Singh%20credited%20legend