patron%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20was%20asked%20to%20act%20as%20the%20gatekeeper%20but%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20random%20excerpts%20of%20individual%20audiences%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERahul%20Dravid%20was%20first%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Is%20there%20any%20explanation%3F%20I%20am%20told%20you%20were%20distracted%20doing%20all%20those%20ads%20for%20some%20engine%20oil.%20That%20is%20not%20your%20job.%20Leave%20such%20marketing%20matters%20to%20Amitabh%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDravid%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20I%20am%20disappointed%2C%20too.%20I%20must%20share%20that%20in%20private%20I%20had%20argued%20very%20strongly%20that%20for%20the%20final%20match%20you%20should%20have%20been%20named%20the%20coach.%20Your%20understanding%20of%20tactics%20and%20reading%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehawa%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20superb.%20But%20I%20was%20overruled%20by%20the%20BCCI%20bosses%2C%20citing%20some%20ICC%20rules%20against%20involvement%20of%20governmental%20functionaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVirat%20Kohli%20is%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Virat.%20How%20is%20Anushka%20taking%20the%20loss%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20go%20so%20slow%3F%20I%20was%20expecting%20a%20century%20from%20you.%20Had%20we%20won%2C%20I%20would%20have%20named%20Ashram%20Road%20after%20you.%20We%20have%20had%20enough%20of%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20you%20have%20always%20been%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20not%20just%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20nation.%20We%20had%20all%20urged%20Rahul%20sir%20to%20rope%20you%20in%20as%20the%20coach%20for%20the%20final.%20But%20I%20suspect%20some%20conspiracy%20against%20you.%20The%20BCCI%20bosses%20were%20bent%20on%20denying%20us%20the%20benefit%20of%20your%20guidance.%20We%20all%20remember%20the%20brilliant%20way%20you%20guided%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20pilots%20on%20how%20to%20attack%20terror%20infrastructure%20in%20POK.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20sir%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20are%20being%20consulted%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20planners%20in%20their%20campaign%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20captain%2C%20was%20next%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rohit.%20Before%20you%20say%20what%20happened%2C%20I%20want%20to%20know%20why%20you%20did%20not%20invite%20me%20to%20your%20wedding%2C%20just%20as%20Virat%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20I%20am%20not%20a%20celebrity%20or%20exhibitionist%20like%20Virat.%20I%20was%20not%20marrying%20a%20celebrity.%20My%20marriage%20was%20my%20affair%2C%20a%20private%20one.%20But%2C%20as%20Rahul%20sir%20must%20have%20told%20you%2C%20I%20was%20very%20keen%20to%20have%20your%20guidance%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%20Nobody%20can%20read%20the%20pitch%20as%20you%20do%2C%20whatever%20the%20arena.%20Nobody%20can%20out-strategise%20the%20rivals%20as%20you%20do.%20Honestly%2C%20sir%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20absence%20of%20your%20guidance%20when%20Head%20was%20refusing%20to%20vacate%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20is%20ushered%20in%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Cem%3E(In%20Gujarati)%3C%2Fem%3E%20Your%20wife%20is%20our%20MLA.%20You%20are%20one%20of%20us.%20Please%20tell%20me%20why%20we%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJadeja%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Saheb%2C%20it%20is%20simple.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20enemies%20hovering%20around%20you.%20The%20entire%20team%20was%20pleading%20for%20your%20ball-to-ball%20guidance.%20But%20the%20BCCI%20brass%20has%20its%20own%20calculations.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20in%20my%20bones%20that%20somehow%20the%20bookies%20ensured%20that%20we%20did%20not%20have%20your%20guidance.%20The%20nexus%20between%20the%20bookies%20and%20the%20BCCI%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMohammed%20Siraj%C2%A0%20was%20ushered%20in%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20have%20given%20so%20much%20space%20to%20you%20people.%20But%20I%20am%20told%20that%20you%20were%20less%20than%20your%20best.%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiraj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Sir%2C%20what%20an%20honour%20to%20meet%20you%20in%20person.%20I%20am%20going%20back%20to%20my%20native%20place%20and%20will%20tell%20everyone%20that%20I%20have%20had%20a%20face-to-face%20meeting%20with%20you.%20Sir%2C%20I%20think%20the%20pitch%20was%20tinkered%20with.%20The%20BCCI%20bosses%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20were%20betting%20on%20the%20Australians.%20%5BThis%20was%5D%20simply%20to%20deny%20you%20the%20glory%20of%20a%20World%20Cup%20during%20your%20leadership.%20Who%20knows%20who%20is%20in%20the%20chair%20at%20the%20next%20Cup%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMohammed%20Shami%20comes%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20put%20out%20that%20shot%20of%20me%20hugging%20you.%20Your%20people%20should%20know%20I%20am%20not%20all%20that%20prejudiced.%C2%A0%20What%20happened%20to%20you%3F%20Why%20only%20one%20wicket%3F%C2%A0%20Why%20could%20you%20not%20reproduce%20the%20magic%20of%20the%20New%20Zealand%20match%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24180806%2Fimage-1538.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221053%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24180806%2Fimage-1538.png%201053w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24180806%2Fimage-15