20informed%20that%20his%20services%20were%20no%20longer%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%20(November%2024)%2C%20Dalsaniya%2C%20along%20with%20his%20elder%20brother%20Mehul%20and%20their%20neighbour%20Bhavesh%20Makwana%2C%20went%20to%20the%20office%20of%20Raniba%20Industries%20on%20Ravapar%20Road%20to%20demand%20his%20salary%20for%20the%20days%20he%20had%20worked%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20their%20arrival%2C%20a%20man%20named%20Om%20Patel%2C%20who%20identified%20himself%20as%20Vibhuti%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20assaulted%20Dalsaniya.%20Subsequently%2C%20Vibhuti%20Patel%2C%20Parixit%20Patel%20(a%20manager%20at%20Raniba%20Industries)%2C%20and%20four%20others%20also%20joined%20in%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20group%20dragged%20Dalsaniya%20to%20an%20elevator%2C%20took%20him%20to%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20commercial%20building%2C%20and%20beat%20him%20up%20with%20a%20belt%20while%20also%20kicking%20and%20punching%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVibhuti%20Patel%20forced%20me%20to%20take%20her%20%3Cem%3Echappal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20my%20mouth%20and%20made%20me%20apologise%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dalsaniya%20said%20in%20his%20complaint.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20threatened%20to%20kill%20me%20if%20I%20came%20to%20Ravapar%20Road%20or%20dared%20to%20file%20a%20complaint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20Dalsaniya%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20state-run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fmaya-sharmas-new-book-explores-the-lives-of-marginalised-lgbt-women-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3EGujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%20Medical%20Education%20and%20Research%20Society%20Hospital%20in%20Morbi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibhuti%20Patel%20and%20her%20employees%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20Sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%2C%20506(2)%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%20143%20(unlawful%20assembly)%2C%20147%20(rioting)%2C%20and%20149%20(every%20member%20of%20an%20unlawful%20assembly%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20committed%20in%20prosecution%20of%20a%20common%20object).%20The%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20has%20also%20been%20invoked%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20Police%20are%20currently%20investigating%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fdalit-man-forced-to-hold-businesswomans-footwear-in-his-mouth-gujarat-police-files-fir%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700834403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F02154556%2FDalit-Lives-Matter-PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgujarat-dalit-man-forced-to-hold-former-employers-footwear-in-mouth-after-asking-for-salary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20businesswoman%20and%20her%20employees%20in%20Morbi%20town.%20The%20police%20are%20currently%20investigating%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgujarat-dalit-man-forced-to-hold-former-employers-footwear-in-mouth-after-asking-for-salary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Berkshire%20Hathaway%20exits%20Paytm%3B%20sells%202.46%25%20stake%20for%20Rs%201%2C371%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700834041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-12%2F19%2Ffull%2F1671433997-0101.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcom