ncreasing.%20Scientists%20reported%202-3%20factors%20for%20this.%20The%20first%20is%20that%20vehicle%20pollution's%20contribution%20is%2036%25.%20The%20second%20factor%20is%20biomass%20burning.%20We%20made%20some%20major%20decisions%20after%20seeing%20this.%20To%20control%20vehicle%20pollution%2C%20we%20issued%20the%20rules%20of%20GRAP%203.%20To%20control%20biomass%20burning%2C%20we%20have%20directed%20the%20related%20organisations%20to%20monitor%20this%20especially.%20especially%20the%20MCD%2C%20Revenue%2C%20DDA%2C%20and%20NDMC%2C%20are%20being%20given%20this%20direction%20for%20the%20fires%20that%20are%20breaking%20out%20at%20various%20places%20in%20the%20parks%2C%26quot%3B%20Gopal%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20for%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20remain%20the%20same%20which%20can%20improve%20after%20November%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiomass%20burning%20will%20increase%20as%20the%20winter%20increases.%20Third%2C%20we%20also%20discussed%20the%20future%20situation.%20For%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20situation%20will%20remain%20the%20same.%20It%20is%20possible%20after%20November%2027%20that%20there%20will%20be%20light%20rain%20and%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20wind%20will%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Gopal%20Rai%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20continued%20to%20hover%20in%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20recorded%20at%20over%20350%20in%20several%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20the%20System%20of%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Weather%20Forecasting%20and%20Research%20(SAFAR-India).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20AQI%20for%20the%20Capital%20was%20recorded%20at%20388%20at%207.55%20am%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20per%20the%20pollution%20numbers%20recorded%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20did%20see%20a%20marginal%20improvement%20from%20th