OCCRP)%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%20cannot%20be%20treated%20as%20gospel%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20raising%20tough%20questions%20on%20demands%20for%20a%20probe%20based%20on%20the%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20had%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20and%20also%20action%20against%20SEBI%20for%20missing%20its%20deadline%20for%20a%20report%20on%20the%20Hindenburg%20case%2C%20faced%20some%20difficult%20questions%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20an%20application%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20for%20an%20inquiry%20into%20allegations%20by%20the%20non-profit%20OCCRP%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OCCRP%2C%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20had%20alleged%20insider%20trading%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20via%20two%20foreign%20investors.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Brecycled%20allegations%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20%26quot%3Bmeritless%20Hindenburg%20report%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20also%20dismissed%20the%20report%20as%20unreliable%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20non-profit%20(NGO)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%2C%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20said%20the%20OCCRP%20had%20sent%20its%20report%20to%20the%20government%20but%20had%20not%20shared%20details.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20that%20they%20can't%20give%20details%20to%20us...%20instead%2C%20they%20directed%20us%20to%20an%20NGO%20linked%20to%20Bhushan.%20This%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20regulation%20will%20become%20meaningless%20if%20we%20start%20looking%20into%20such%20self-serving%20reports%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20lawyer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20SEBI%20missing%20the%20deadline%2C%20he%20said%20the%20regulator%20had%20exceeded%20it%20by%20just%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Bhushan%2C%20defending%20his%20charge%20against%20SEBI%2C%20said%20it%20had%20a%20letter%20in%202014%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20alleging%20over-invoicing%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%20but%20had%20never%20acted%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20lawyer%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20DRI%20had%20completed%20the%20probe%20in%202017%20and%20had%20found%20no%20irregularities.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20problem%20when%20they%20rely%20on%20random%20information%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20confirmed%20the%20DRI%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20told%20Mr%20Bhushan%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20careful.%20We%20are%20not%20giving%20any%20character%20certificates.%20We%20can't%20make%20random%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20also%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20committee%20of%20domain%20experts%20appointed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20look%20into%20India's%20regulatory%20mechanism%20to%20protect%20investors.%20The%20judges%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20members%20were%20selected%20by%20the%20top%20court%2C%20not%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Bhushan%20pressed%20on%20about%20SEBI%20not%20acting%20on%20reports%20by%20the%20OCCRP%20and%20published%20in%20foreign%20media%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20discrediting%20what's%20reported%20on%20FT%2C%20Guardian%2C%20but%20does%20it%20have%20evidentiary%20value%20for%20SEBI%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20journalists%20could%20get%20hold%20of%20documents%2C%20argued%20Mr%20Bhushan%2C%20why%20couldn't%20SEBI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSEBI%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20laws%20of%20evidentiary%20value.%20SEBI%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20appellate%20authorities.%20SEBI%20can't%20say%20we%20relied%20on%20newspaper%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20firmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20rely%20on%20the%20newspaper%20stories%3F%20How%20do%20we%20say%20these%20are%20credible%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20stories%20were%20being%20planted%20outside%20India%20to%20influence%20policies%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20said%20there%20are%20overwhelming%20evidence.%20What%20are%20those%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%20Mr%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20cited%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20treat%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20as%20the%20true%20state%20of%20affairs.%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20why%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20publication's%20work%20cannot%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20gospel%20of%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20in%20its%20report%20in%20May%20had%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20It%20had%20said%20there%20was%20no%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20SEBI%2C%20and%20no%20price%20manipulation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20that%20the%20conglomerate%20had%20taken%20necessary%20steps%20to%20comfort%20retail%20investors%20amid%20severe%20market%20turmoil%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700831580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-08%2Fi5g4f5g8_prashant-bhushan-afp-2019_650x