20would%20not%20seek%20an%20extension%20to%20complete%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20you%20found%20any%20wrongdoing%20on%20the%20part%20of%20short-selling%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20the%20government%20was%20taking%20action%20%26quot%3Bwherever%20we%20have%20found%20short%20selling%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20suggestions%20from%20the%20expert%20committee%20on%20the%20ways%20to%20strengthen%20the%20regulatory%20framework.%20Regarding%20the%20suggestions%20of%20the%20expert%20committee%20on%20strengthening%20the%20regulatory%20framework%20we%20don't%20have%20any%20objections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20raised%20tough%20questions%20on%20a%20demand%20by%20senior%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20for%20action%20against%20SEBI%20for%20not%20completing%20its%20report%20within%20the%20court's%20deadline%20and%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20allegations%20by%20George%20Soros-funded%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20SEBI%20also%20dismissed%20the%20report%20as%20unreliable%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20non-profit%20(NGO)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OCCRP%20had%20alleged%20insider%20trading%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20via%20two%20foreign%20investors.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Brecycled%20allegations%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20%26quot%3Bmeritless%20Hindenburg%20report%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20said%20when%20details%20were%20sought%20from%20OCCRP%2C%20they%20directed%20the%20queries%20to%20an%20NGO%20linked%20to%20Prashant%20Bhushan.%20%26quot%3BThey%20