%3Cp%3EA%20top%20bureaucrat%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20make%20a%20fresh%20investment%20call%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20after%20noticing%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%20at%20the%20BGBS%E2%80%9D.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0could%20not%20independently%20verify%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20conspicuous%20by%20its%20absence%20during%20the%20BGBS%2C%20even%20though%20the%20group%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20previous%20editions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20criticism%20from%20many%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20TMC%2C%20for%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20irregular%20practices%2C%20including%20stock%20price%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20months%20following%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20power%20in%202021%20had%20seen%20growing%20proximity%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20group.%20Gautam%20and%20Karan%20Adani%20had%20separately%20met%20the%20chief%20minister%20on%20different%20occasions%20%E2%80%93%20Gautam%20Adani%20in%20December%202021%20and%20Karan%20Adani%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fkaran-adani-meets-west-bengal-cm-mamata-banerjee-chief-secretary-at-nabanna%2Farticleshow%2F89493607.cms%5C%22%3EFebruary%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fmamata-hands-over-tajpur-ports-letter-of-intent-to-karan-adani%2Farticleshow%2F94817328.cms%5C%22%3EOctober%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20after%20meeting%20Banerjee%2C%20Adani%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1466409022970499073%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20discussed%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%20investment%20scenarios%20and%20the%20tremendous%20potential%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%20Five%20months%20later%2C%20at%20the%20previous%20BGBS%20edition%20in%20April%202022%2C%20Adani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2FMedia-Coverage%2F2022%2F20220421-HBL-Adani-to-invest-over-10000-cr-in-Bengal.pdf%3Fla%3Den%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20summit%20that%20their%20investment%20in%20the%20state%20would%20exceed%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20said%20that%20the%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccommitting%20to%20bring%20technology%20and%20scale%20to%20create%20world-class%20infrastructure%2C%20data%20centres%2C%20centres%20of%20excellence%20for%20digital%20innovation%2C%20under-sea%20cable%20and%20warehousing%20and%20logistics%20park%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20bagging%20the%20LoI%2C%20the%20group%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FInvestor-Downloads%2FQuarterly-Results%2FOutcomeofBoardMeeting.pdf%5C%22%3Elaunched%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20new%2C%20wholly-owned%20subsidiary%2C%20Tajpur%20Sagar%20Port%20Limited%2C%20incorporated%20on%20October%2021%2C%202022.%20The%20group%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FTranscripts%2FQ2-FY23-Transcript.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0it%20expected%20to%20commission%20the%20project%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20had%2C%20quite%20curiously%2C%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20Tajpur%20port%20%E2%80%93%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20industrial%20project%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%202023%20budget%2C%20even%20though%20the%20government%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.wb.gov.in%2Fwritereaddata%2FBudget_Speech%2F2022_English.pdf%5C%22%3Ehad%20mentioned