.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeath%20penalty%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20eight%20Indian%20employees%20of%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20a%20now-defunct%20Omani%20firm.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20Indian%20employees%20were%20former%20Indian%20naval%20officers%20who%20had%20been%20recruited%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20the%20Qatari%20defence%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20the%20appeal%20has%20been%20accepted%20and%20the%20hearings%20for%20the%20application%20will%20start%20as%20per%20schedule.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20other%20details%20were%20provided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20men%20are%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%2C%20Commodore%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commodore%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commodore%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20they%20were%20apprehended%20without%20any%20formal%20charges%2C%20and%20media%20accounts%20indicated%20that%20they%20were%20being%20accused%20of%20espionage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20family%20members%20had%20been%20vocal%20in%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20till%20last%20year%2C%20but%20have%20preferred%20to%20remain%20silent%20for%20months%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20matter%20became%20public%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20in%20public%20that%20the%20case%20requires%20%E2%80%9Csensitive%E2%80%9D%20handling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20death%20penalty%20verdict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20embass