eniors%20to%20let%20me%20perform%20on%20stage%20and%20they%20would%20give%20me%20a%20chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20as%20he%20was%20coming%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20Anthropology%2C%20he%20began%20performing%20in%20front%20of%20live%20audiences%20and%20earning%20some%20money%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20has%20always%20been%20supportive%20of%20my%20music.%20During%20my%20college%20days%2C%20I%20never%20flunked%20out%2C%20brought%20bad%20grades%20or%20got%20held%20up%20by%20%E2%80%98back%20papers%E2%80%99.%20That%20allowed%20my%20family%20to%20trust%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20with%20my%20life.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20making%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20making%20music%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20but%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20passion.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20performed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20live%20audience%20and%20got%20paid%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20can%20pursue%20music%20as%20a%20professional%20career%20instead%20of%20studying%2C%20giving%20exams%2C%20and%20pursuing%20government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20any%20artist%20starting%20out%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20pay%20for%20studio%20sessions%20when%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20Early%20on%2C%20Moko%20would%20borrow%20money%20from%20his%20mother%20to%20pay%20for%20these%20sessions%20because%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20proper%20recording%20studio%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26u