as%20introduced%20me%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20audience%2C%20particularly%20the%20older%20generations.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20recognised%20that%20not%20everyone%20has%20the%20voice%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20community.%20As%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20have%20that%20platform.%20So%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20address%20some%20key%20social%20issues%20in%20Nagaland%20like%20alcohol%20prohibition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20we%20talk%20about%20something%20very%20serious%2C%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20usually%20listen.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20bringing%20in%20some%20humour%20so%20that%20people%20would%20listen.%20This%20helped%20me%20establish%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20song%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvylA2NHVCIo%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FvylA2NHVCIo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20exposed%20a%20whole%20new%20audience%20to%20Moko%E2%80%99s%20music%20and%20provided%20some%20interesting%20insights%20into%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer