iness-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20or%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20connected%20to%20food%20and%20I%20really%20enjoy%20being%20around%20children.%20You%20learn%20something%20new%20in%20both%20teaching%20and%20cooking.%20Every%20day%20is%20a%20new%20day%20in%20the%20kitchen%20as%20well%20as%20the%20classroom.%20I%20love%20it.%20Why%20would%20I%20choose%20between%20the%20two%3F%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nambie%20Jessica%20Marak%20from%20Meghalaya%20created%20'Eat%20Your%20Kappa'%20on%20YouTube%20to%20showcase%20Northeastern%20culture%20and%20change%20how%20people%20view%20local%20food.%20She's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20top-eight%20finalists%20on%20MasterChef%20India%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334658%2Fnambie-jessica-marak-masterchef-india-finalist-northeastern-food-meghalaya-chef-eat-your-kappa%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Iconic%20Food%20Businesses%20of%20India%20That%20Are%20Over%2050%20Years%20Old%20%26amp%3B%20Thriving%20as%20Multicrore%20Ventures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEveryone%20knows%20Vadilal%2C%20Balaji%20and%20Parle-G%20today.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20grown%20up%20eating%20their%20snacks%20and%20confectioneries.%20But%20few%20know%20the%20story%20of%20their%20humble%20beginnings.%20Born%20in%20small%20rooms%20and%20fields%2C%20these%20businesses%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334480%2Ffem-tech-startup-for-women-mind-and-mom-by-padmini-janaki-pregnancy-ivf-consultation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E