es%20traditional%20Kashmiri%20ingredients%20in%20creative%2C%20restaurant-quality%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20chef%20thanks%20to%20MasterChef.%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20it%20all%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20one%20of%20the%20few%20Kashmiri%20women%20chefs%2C%20Rukhsaar%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20inspiration%20for%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20valley.%20She%20urges%20youngsters%20to%20follow%20their%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20career%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20my%20passion%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20youngsters%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20to%20transform%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20career.%20Have%20faith%20in%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20her%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98aha%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoment%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20day%20she%20felt%20%E2%80%98she%20made%20it%E2%80%99%2C%20despite%20achieving%20so%20much%2C%20Rukhsaar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20day%20is%20yet%20to%20come%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20a%20good%20place%20and%20very%20grateful%20for%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20received%20so%20far.%20But%20I%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20do.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20truly%20ever%20wanted%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20wait%20to%20see%20the%20heights%20that%20this%20fiery%20woman%20reaches%2C%20you%20can%20follow%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkhalis_foods%2F%3Fhl%3